description.content:
Hello,


I am Noor Muhammad . Thank You for looking my services. I'm offering the services of creating dynamic Page in React JS with backend/API Integration . I have 5+ years of experience in JavaScript/ React JS development. During my experience, I have worked on 500+ React JS Projects.


  • I WILL Develop NFT Landing Pages or NFT Website .
  • NFT Minting website
  • Modern NFT Landing Page Design
  • Modern Mint Page

Following are the services I'm offering in this gig:


  • React JS App development (Classes and Functional based components).
  • PSD/ XD/ FIGMA to React JS development
  • Backend/ APIs integration.
  • Backend development in Node Js/ mySQL/ MongoDB.
  • nft minting , nft marketplace , minting landing page design
  • Material UI/ Ant design/ Bootstrap 5
  • Responsive App/ Mobile Friendly/ Animations
  • NFT Website Design and Your NFT idea into Design

and much more..


Also, I will convert your FIGMA,XD design into Responsive React JS Website


Your satisfaction is my first priority, I always try my best to provide best services of mine to my customer.

Thanks,


BONUS: I will host your website for free on NETLIFY or Google Firebase and surge.


IF you have any questions Feel free to ask.


Regards : Noor Muhammad
